"Niba uri hanze ya USA, turagusaba NOWPayments (amafaranga agabanya cyane, "
"byihutirwa ku mafaranga yawe). Niba uri muri USA, Stripe Crypto ni naho "
"ushobora kuyikoresha. Ushobora kwemerera serivisi nyinshi kandi wemerere "
"abashyitsi bawe guhitamo!"

