msgid ""
"A powerful, free donation and payment widget that allows your visitors to "
"support you via credit card or cryptocurrency (Quai). No monthly fees, no "
"third-party subscriptions – just your wallet and free services."
msgstr ""
"Igikoresho gikomeye, cy'ubuntu cyo gutanga no kwishyura, gituma abasura bawe"
" bashobora kukwerekana inkunga ukoresheje ikadi ya kredit cyangwa "
"cryptocurrency (Quai). Nta mafaranga y'ukwezi, nta gahunda z'abandi – gusa "
"gikapu cyawe n'ibikorwa by'ubuntu."

msgid ""
"Some browsers block third-party scripts for privacy. This proxy loads "
"scripts through your own server to bypass these blocks."
msgstr ""
"Bimwe mu bisomero byirinda scripts zituruka ahandi kubera ubwisanzure. Proxy"
" yacu itwara scripts ukoresheje server yawe kugira ngo uce aya makosa."

msgid ""
"You can update the script URLs below if the original URLs change or if you "
"want to use a different CDN."
msgstr ""
"Urashobora kuvugurura aderesi za script hano hasi niba aderesi z'inkomoko "
"zahindutse cyangwa niba wifuza gukoresha CDN itandukanye."

